      • importContracts

        public RequestResponse importContracts(InputStream contracts,
                                       Integer tenantId,
                                       AdminCollections collection)
                                throws InvalidParseOperationException
        Description copied from interface: AdminExternalClient
        Import a set of contracts after passing the validation steps. If all the contracts are valid, they are stored in the collection and indexed.
        The input is invalid in the following situations :
        • The json is invalid
        • The json contains 2 ore many contracts having the same name
        • One or more mandatory field is missing
        • A field has an invalid format
        • One or many contracts elready exist in the database
